name: PUREFILTH Magazine Vol. 7.5  Featuring VIZIE MSK & Magena Yama by Corrado Dalco
description:
The Seventh Volume of PUREFILTH is now available for Pre-Order.

Featuring Magena Yama by Corrado Dalco, graffiti by VIZIE, and highlights from the Austin graffiti and skate scenes spotlighting the photography of Mr.Glass, Drew Pickell, and more. 
Also features a new Quinn Cornchip section.

A special gift will be available with each purchase, more details soon.

Edition of 75 / Hand Numbered.
86 Pages B+W with some color.
8.5"x11" with Saddle Stitched binding.
Printed in USA

name: PUREFILTH Magazine Vol. 6.5 Featuring Shay Laren By Ellen Stagg & Mike GIANT
description:
Now Available.

The sixth issue of PUREFILTH Magazine features adult star; Shay Laren by esteemed NYC photographer; Ellen Stagg and Graffiti photography by Mike GIANT. Issue also features interviews with Mike Giant and Ellen Stagg, Austin graffiti highlights from Mr.Glass, and skate photography by Drew Pickel and Shaun Mefford.

Edition of 50 Hand-Numbered
64 pages
B+W printing on premium matte paper.
8.5"x11"
Saddle Stitched Binding

Comes packaged in a re-closable bag with a custom temporary tattoo set designed by Mike GIANT for PUREFILTH.

name: PUREFILTH Magazine Vol. 5.5  TILT Cover Featuring Hattie Watson & Mr.Glass & TILT
description:
The Fifth Edition of PUREFILTH Magazine features Hattie Watson by Mr.Glass of Heels&Candy.com, and Grafiiti and Photography by TILT.

name: PUREFILTH Magazine Subscription Service
description:
PUREFILTH is a fully independent, art based publisher.
 By becoming a subscription member, you are helping us meet our goal of printing 4 Volumes of PUREFILTH a year, along with it's sister publication; FuckingDelicious!.
 On top of that, members receive a personalized code for discounted purchases, the first updates on upcoming releases, new products, and also receive exclusive content from the PUREFILTH blog.

Free t-shirt with Subscription. Actual t-shirt varies per order. Be sure to include your size in the "Instructions To Seller" menu when checking out.


*Please note, shipping charges are for all four issues.
* Please allow 4-6 weeks for delivery.
